{"tid":127962,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"牛扒慢煮真係好食d?","createTime":"2017-02-20T12:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T11:21:01.000Z","uid":32534,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10a126f147a0b6daf7fb1052f9614a8a81ed5cf7","tid":127962,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"浸成個幾鐘，搞到黎要2個鐘先有得食，仲要買成千蚊工具，值得嗎？"},{"pid":"091c1026d9bb53e599f5a6280fe5f66d62ca5461","tid":127962,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"早兩粒鐘煮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮既時候你都可以做第二d野既"},{"pid":"6657fae0e2eb9d79074300f616bd799bf3c9a679","tid":127962,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩粒鐘煮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮既時候你都可以做第二d野既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n值得嗎？youtube 好多教學都係就咁煎，都好靚仔"},{"pid":"d5709411a5b8a051fa88b064b84f7e08dc469e78","tid":127962,"uid":11641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"港奴OT到佛誕又點有時間同你慢煮？"},{"pid":"1cc1cce8cb985610519e5e2c0ee43c1610c7fb13","tid":127962,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"慢咪嫩口啲 同佢可以封死肉汁"},{"pid":"81c276392b93c33ac70e20e555c097e9aa82797a","tid":127962,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"肉質會均勻好多，食落冇咁辛苦，但食開生嘅感覺上會更生，食開三成食慢煮要嗌五成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce28057141e07be03ba9a1e58ea319a6d1dd3e15","tid":127962,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"好食係因為可以好易咁控制到成塊有幾熟, 一定唔會 over<br />\n你平時煎, 外邊果層點都會熟過裡面<br />\n<br />\n我自己平時慢煮用54-56度, 煮完再會用火槍封燒, 成塊都好嫩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過慢煮用果D扒買厚身D 好D, 因為封煎果下太薄都會易 over"},{"pid":"d2982e65a2e99835e3d76b9f4c53c3600ee8d6a2","tid":127962,"uid":50550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早兩粒鐘煮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮既時候你都可以做第二d野既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n值得嗎？youtube 好多教學都係就咁煎，都好靚仔</blockquote><br />\n煎會香口D, 慢煮嫩口D, 睇你鍾意<br />\n<br />\n情況如炸薯條定焗薯咁樣, 冇話邊樣好食<br />\n時間既野, 喜歡的話10個鐘都覺得短, 不喜歡1分鐘都係長<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"682da96651fe8d3da2e9d732b9745edadec645ae","tid":127962,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"高級西餐嘅嘢 你識咩吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛排2個鐘<br />\n食 法國餐 食5個鐘見過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f9da561b4a6e0dff123a7f6a05df75f2d93b3","tid":127962,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高級西餐嘅嘢 你識咩吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛排2個鐘<br />\n食 法國餐 食5個鐘見過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚未食過高級西餐，最貴一次都係食BLT，叫5成都係硬撚過石"},{"pid":"854271f7d59f358e562799d80338938a43c8498e","tid":127962,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好食係因為可以好易咁控制到成塊有幾熟, 一定唔會 over<br />\n你平時煎, 外邊果層點都會熟過裡面<br />\n<br />\n我自己平時慢煮用54-56度, 煮完再會用火槍封燒, 成塊都好嫩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過慢煮用果D扒買厚身D 好D, 因為封煎果下太薄都會易 over</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好大工程"},{"pid":"c68023c4b90fb01e3d29e161e583643af7f3a6cf","tid":127962,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好食係因為可以好易咁控制到成塊有幾熟, 一定唔會 over<br />\n你平時煎, 外邊果層點都會熟過裡面<br />\n<br />\n我自己平時慢煮用54-56度, 煮完再會用火槍封燒, 成塊都好嫩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過慢煮用果D扒買厚身D 好D, 因為封煎果下太薄都會易 over</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好大工程</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有幾大? 同埋煮扒一般一個鐘咩都夠<br />\nD 扒你可以平時真空 pack 定放冰格, 要食果時早一晚放上雪櫃解凍<br />\n我果枝 Anova 慢煮捧可以 wifi remote 預熱定D水, 返屋企就咁掉塊扒落水就搞掂"},{"pid":"741de2fe94b60ab36d75c337f065b4881a4f973a","tid":127962,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早兩粒鐘煮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮既時候你都可以做第二d野既</blockquote><br />\n全日係屋企鳩hea咪係，要返工返學或者下午有約既話返到屋企都七八點。"},{"pid":"e5cc29f07f65a4f84e8f8d00e028d00d697b2e7a","tid":127962,"uid":32534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早兩粒鐘煮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮既時候你都可以做第二d野既</blockquote><br />\n全日係屋企鳩hea咪係，要返工返學或者下午有約既話返到屋企都七八點。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6-7點放工，去買舊扒，煮到黎都10點。真係食扒都要早一日計劃定<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80a100991d7cf59b471ff3503ac1a1b8a951aea","tid":127962,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"出去食咪得"},{"pid":"0e97e19359874c464a6fb9fafa97fd3e65b7a99c","tid":127962,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出去食咪得</blockquote><br />\noutback都有"},{"pid":"db13b180077d51931803200af05cfc4bfea8f062","tid":127962,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"根本唔駛, 睇大城小廚學<br />\n大火煎兩邊<br />\n每一邊煎既時後搵蓋煎住焗6-7弟鐘(厚扒）<br />\n搞完兩邊就食得"},{"pid":"32ee1a5e8fd59e708bb245db174a352c1e7ae344","tid":127962,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慢咪嫩口啲 同佢可以封死肉汁</blockquote><br />\n應係大火快先可以封肉汁"},{"pid":"e86c2d3ad634ddbe8eb4cbbe0d1a5df6a4c664f1","tid":127962,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔駛, 睇大城小廚學<br />\n大火煎兩邊<br />\n每一